'''Jawa Traders''' was a store in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] which specialized in [[Starship/Legends|starship]]- and vehicle-repairing [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. Due to this, the store was a source of income in a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] that was rich in [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] and other sorts of unsavory clientèle. The shop was owned and managed by the [[Jawa/Legends|Jawa]] [[Aguilae]], who later hired a [[Squib/Legends|Squib]], [[Macemillian-winduarté]], to help her for she discovered that she had difficulties parting with her own merchandise. For a short time Jawa Traders owned the accounting droid [[CZ-3/Legends|CZ-3]].<ref name="GG7" />

